com.tozny.e3db

Class SearchRequest.SearchRange

  • Object
    • com.tozny.e3db.SearchRequest.SearchRange
  • Enclosing class:
    SearchRequest

    public static class SearchRequest.SearchRange
extends Object
    The window in which a search should occur SearchRangeType specifies if the range should use RecordMeta.created() RecordMeta.lastModified() by using SearchRequest.SearchRangeType.CREATED and SearchRequest.SearchRangeType.MODIFIED respectively If start is null the search range will be unbounded from the beginning of time. If end is null the search range will be unbounded from start to all time in the future
